# Canonical source / actor definitions — photographs, recordings, diaries and
# the people/units they involve. Chapters reference these by id (nmg:references,
# nmg:cites, nmg:depicts, nmg:derivedFrom, …); they no longer define their own.
@prefix nmg:    <https://nijmegenkaart.nl/ns#> .
@prefix id:     <https://nijmegenkaart.nl/id/> .
@prefix schema: <http://schema.org/> .
@prefix dct:    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix owl:    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs:   <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd:    <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix wd:     <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> .

